verbose_text: As shown in Table XREF_TABLE, PCa patients with MYPT1-low / CD31-high expression more frequently had higher Gleason score (P = 0.004), higher pathological stage (P = 0.047), positive biochemical recurrence (P = 0.022), and shorter overall survival (P = 0.031) than those with other combination of MYPT1 / CD31 expression.
